title: RHOA: A Strip of a Lifetime - Plus: Top Chef
description:
The women of "Real Housewives of Atlanta" are still in Japan, and this week they get a visit from a very special stripper who doesn't exactly knock their socks off. Or his own. We recap the whole shebang, and then after we move on to "Top Chef" to laugh about the things we missed in last week's show. Enjoy!

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
